@startuml estados-ordem
!theme plain
title Diagrama de Estados — Ciclo de Vida de uma Ordem

[*] --> NEW : Ordem criada\n(saldo reservado)

NEW --> PARTIALLY_FILLED : Match parcial\n(remaining > 0)
NEW --> FILLED : Match completo\n(remaining == 0)
NEW --> CANCELLED : Cancelamento\n(saldo liberado)

PARTIALLY_FILLED --> PARTIALLY_FILLED : Novo match parcial\n(remaining > 0)
PARTIALLY_FILLED --> FILLED : Match completa\n  remaining restante\n(remaining == 0)
PARTIALLY_FILLED --> CANCELLED : Cancelamento\n(remaining liberado)

FILLED --> [*]
CANCELLED --> [*]

note right of NEW
  Saldo reservado:
  BUY: price * quantity em BRL
  SELL: quantity em Vibranium
end note

note right of PARTIALLY_FILLED
  remaining rastreia quanto
  ainda falta preencher.
  Cada trade reduz remaining.
end note

note right of FILLED
  Ordem totalmente executada.
  Saldo ja transferido via trades.
  Estado terminal — imutavel.
end note

note right of CANCELLED
  Saldo do remaining
  devolvido ao usuario.
  Estado terminal — imutavel.
end note
@enduml
